title: Charles Bukowski - A collection of Audio Recordings
description:
This is a collection of poetry readings and other Buk related material that I've compiled over time. I doubt that it's complete, but I've yet to find something better out there. Enjoy!

Contents

70 Minutes in Hell (1969)
At Terror Street and Agony Way (1969)
King of Poets (1970)
Poems and Insults (1973)
Solid Citizen (1978)
Hostage (1980)
Charles Bukowski Reads 'Do You Use a Notebook' (1986)
Run With the Hunted (1993)
Bukowski Lives!
Neither Bought for Gold, Nor to the Devil Sold - The Life and Hazardous Times of Charles Bukowski
Uncensored
Wilem van Ekeren - Bach-Bukowski (2002)
